window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>Some things are better left forgotten.</i></b></p> <p>Dreams taunt me, filling me with questions even more so than the supernatural world I’d only just learned about. Making matters worse, a vampire attacked me while I was alone in the middle of the night.</p> <p>Death was imminent until a silver wolf saved me.</p> <p>A silver wolf who shifted into the most gorgeous man I'd ever seen, and no matter how hard I try to ignore it, there’s something pulling me toward him.</p> <p>Secrets come to light, and nothing is as it seemed.</p> <p>I'm being hunted.</p> <p>The silver wolf vows to protect me, no matter the cost, but the stakes are becoming too high. Not only are we fighting an unseen enemy, but we're battling the forbidden attraction between us.</p> <p>Leaving the only home I've ever known behind, I’m forced to face my destiny as the ones I love struggle to stay alive.</p> <p><b><i>Scroll up and buy this suspenseful fated-mates wolf-shifter story today.</i></b></p>"; 
